step_original: Certificate of authenticity: Certificate of authenticity fresh 'EMPEROR' table grapes
step_description: Provide a certificate of authenticity for fresh 'EMPEROR' table grapes
step_howto_description: A certificate of authenticity will need to be provided by a competent authority from the exporting country, certifying that the grapes being imprted are fresh table grapes of the variety 'Emperor' (Vitis vinifera cv).
